sub_title: Grow and improve your audience engagement thanks to data-driven marketing tools tailor-made for cultural venues
summary:
In the past 10 years I have been involved in the production, the coordination and the communication of artistic projects in several cultural industries (performing arts, film, street arts). 
I had the chance to build a rich professionnal experience in 4 different countries (France, Turkey, Germany, the Netherlands). What I have learned within these work environments has broaden my understanding of the cultural sector.
I am convinced that digital tools have great potential for cultural institutions and initiatives: to reach a broader audience thanks to online sales & multichannel targeted communication, but also to get a better understanding of their visitors.
I am very much interested in the application of digital tools serving marketing purposes, and also of tools supporting art education projects. 
I believe both marketing and art education strategies can strongly contribute to a vivid connection between artistic productions and audiences.
